		"title"		: "A Tale of Two Beasts",
		"text"		: "1\n00:00:03,120 --> 00:00:08,080\nWelcome to Storyline Online, brought to you by the SAG-AFTRA Foundation.\n\n2\n00:00:08,200 --> 00:00:18,540\nI'm Sarah Silverman, and today I'm going to read \"A Tale of Two Beasts,\" written and illustrated by Fiona Roberton.\n\n3\n00:00:18,540 --> 00:00:25,720\nI was walking home from Grandma's house, through the deep dark woods, when I spied a strange little beast...\n\n4\n00:00:26,480 --> 00:00:28,460\nFeep, feep, feep, feep\n\n5\n00:00:29,580 --> 00:00:32,920\nHe was stuck up a tree, and whining sadly\n\n6\n00:00:32,920 --> 00:00:35,660\nso I decided to rescue him.\n\n7\n00:00:36,480 --> 00:00:36,980\nFeep!\n\n8\n00:00:38,040 --> 00:00:40,880\n\"I will call you Fang!\" I told him,\n\n9\n00:00:41,760 --> 00:00:44,720\nand I wrapped him warmly up in my scarf,\n\n10\n00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:47,740\nand carried him safely home.\n\n11\n00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:54,480\nI gave him a lovely bath, and a gorgeous new hat and sweater,\n\n12\n00:00:54,480 --> 00:00:57,400\nand a delicious bowl of fresh nuts.\n\n13\n00:00:58,760 --> 00:01:03,840\nI made him a beautiful house, and gave him Lord Rex to play with.\n\n14\n00:01:04,580 --> 00:01:08,520\nLord Rex is her stuffed lion, it looks like.\n\n15\n00:01:10,220 --> 00:01:17,460\nI took him out for lots of long walkies to keep him fit and healthy.\n\n16\n00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:26,060\nAnd I showed him off to all of my friends, who loved him nearly as much as I did.\n\n17\n00:01:26,060 --> 00:01:28,440\n-Ooh!\n-Amazing!\n\n18\n00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:31,380\n-Awesome!\n-He's so cute!\n\n19\n00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:36,560\nBut for some strange reason, the little beast did not look very happy.\n\n20\n00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:40,180\nIn fact, he was looking rather hot.\n\n21\n00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:45,600\n'I hope he's not sick,' I thought, and opened the window to cool him down.\n\n22\n00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:50,000\nBut then something terrible happened!\n\n23\n00:01:50,660 --> 00:01:58,600\nHe threw off his clothes, leapt out of the window, and ran away as fast as he could, back to the deep dark woods.\n\n24\n00:01:59,000 --> 00:01:59,500\nFang!\n\n25\n00:02:00,440 --> 00:02:02,520\nFeep, feep, feep, feep!\n\n26\n00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:06,500\nI wanted to go look for him, but Mama had other plans.\n\n27\n00:02:06,900 --> 00:02:09,340\nDinnertime! Blurgh!\n\n28\n00:02:10,760 --> 00:02:13,400\nBathtime! Uuurgh!\n\n29\n00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:16,000\nBedtime! Grrrgh!\n\n30\n00:02:18,160 --> 00:02:23,480\nI couldn't sleep. I missed the little beast, and wondered if I would ever see him again.\n\n31\n00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:30,420\nBut then a small furry shadow appeared at the foot of my bed.\n\n32\n00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:34,880\nThe strange little beast had returned.\n\n33\n00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:45,400\nHe seemed quite pleased to see me, and I began to think that maybe, just maybe...\n\n34\n00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:48,560\n...he wasn't that strange after all.\n\n35\n00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,680\nI wonder why he came back?\n\n36\n00:02:56,880 --> 00:03:00,020\nA Tale of Two Beasts, Part Two:\n\n37\n00:03:00,340 --> 00:03:02,160\nThe Terrible Beast.\n\n38\n00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:07,620\nTra la la la la, tra la la la la\n\n39\n00:03:07,620 --> 00:03:13,860\nI was hanging from my favorite tree, singing happily to the birds when...\n\n40\n00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:15,500\nHey!\n\n41\n00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:19,580\nI was ambushed by a terrible beast!\n\n42\n00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:20,380\nGrowf!\n\n43\n00:03:20,900 --> 00:03:27,380\nShe growled at me, and tied me up, and carried me off to her secret lair.\n\n44\n00:03:27,660 --> 00:03:31,160\nShe made me disgustingly clean, gross!\n\n45\n00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:39,260\nand dressed me up in a ridiculous hat and sweater, and tried to make me eat squirrel food. Yuck!\n\n46\n00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:45,560\nShe kept me in a tiny box, with nothing for me to do and nowhere for me to hang from.\n\n47\n00:03:47,540 --> 00:03:54,020\nShe made me walk backwards, and forwards, and backwards again, for no reason whatsoever.\n\n48\n00:03:57,340 --> 00:04:03,760\nShe showed me off to a herd of even wilder beasts, who were just as terrible as she was.\n\n49\n00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,840\nI had had enough!\n\n50\n00:04:06,860 --> 00:04:10,780\nI made a cunning plan, and put it straight into action.\n\n51\n00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:16,320\na + b = freedom, yes!\n\n52\n00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:17,820\nGrowf!\n\n53\n00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,560\nWoohoo!\n\n54\n00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,360\nThe deep dark woods, 1 mile\n\n55\n00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:24,120\nFree once more!\n\n56\n00:04:24,820 --> 00:04:29,660\nI raced back to the deep dark woods, before the terrible beast could catch me.\n\n57\n00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,660\nScritch scratch\n\n58\n00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:34,840\nIt was peaceful in the deep dark woods,\n\n59\n00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:37,900\na bit too peaceful perhaps.\n\n60\n00:04:39,420 --> 00:04:41,280\nSilence.\n\n61\n00:04:42,580 --> 00:04:45,300\nAnd also, a bit wet.\n\n62\n00:04:47,440 --> 00:04:52,920\nIn weather like this one could do with a nice warm hat.\n\n63\n00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:57,600\nI snuck back to retrieve it under cover of darkness.\n\n64\n00:04:59,980 --> 00:05:03,000\nThe terrible beast was waiting for me.\n\n65\n00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:13,920\nShe seemed quite pleased to see me, and I began to think that maybe, just maybe...\n\n66\n00:05:17,220 --> 00:05:20,300\n...she wasn't that terrible after all.\n\n67\n00:05:20,900 --> 00:05:22,680\nThe end.\n\n68\n00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:30,640\nI love this book. I chose to read this book because everybody has a different way of seeing the same thing.\n\n69\n00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:33,280\nAnd that's how it is in life, with everything.\n\n70\n00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:39,900\nThe way you see something is completely different from the way your friend sees something, or your mom sees something.\n\n71\n00:05:40,140 --> 00:05:45,460\nAnd to get to see both characters' point of view is cool.\n\n72\n00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:49,340\nThank you for watching Storyline Online.\n\n73\n00:05:49,340 --> 00:05:55,280\nMake sure you check out all of our stories, and keep watching, and keep reading.",
